subtypes: MusicalAlbum, Broadcast, PeriodicalPublisher, ProductionCompany, TVNetwork, AwardNominee, AwardWinner, FilmDirector, FilmProducer, MusicalArtist, TVProducer
title: BBC News Review: Parents saying 'no' to vaccinations
description:
More families in America aren't taking their children to get vaccinations. Experts say it could lead to the spread of measles, as has happened in Europe. 

Neil and Catherine teach you how to use the language the world's media is using to discuss this story.

For more, visit our website: http://www.bbc.co.uk/learningenglish/english/course/english-you-need/unit-10/session-2
